{"id": 1233, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得职场上比你更年轻的人有啥特点？", "description": "是长江后浪推前浪，还是一代更比一代丧？（题图来自：John F. Malta）", "record_count": 3435, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160920165901Qba8d4IBWwtN1ePK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 121792, "content": "真敢花钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 305, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 117856, "content": "心大，怎么说辞职就辞职了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 325, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 117884, "content": "好像工作没有我们努力，比我们更排斥加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 174, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 121802, "content": "就剩下一股傻劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724878}, {"id": 121804, "content": "就是几年前的我~ 大概……可能", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676353}, {"id": 121856, "content": "永无休止地重复而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779666}, {"id": 123392, "content": "没有辣么踏实和细心，但是也有很多想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779560}, {"id": 121858, "content": "除了与自己有关的事，其它的都漠不关心", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695493}, {"id": 125698, "content": "活力与朝气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800655}, {"id": 121859, "content": "没毕业 来吸取经验?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754440}, {"id": 121860, "content": "经常被批，可啥事都想发表个人意见，活在自我的世界里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786646}, {"id": 121861, "content": "抗压能力不够。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782075}, {"id": 121862, "content": "蠢而懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626154}, {"id": 121863, "content": "家里不缺钱，凭兴趣做这份工", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 121868, "content": "我就是那个新来的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786689}, {"id": 121869, "content": "安于现状，不知所谓，没追求", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777333}, {"id": 121870, "content": "最年轻的就是我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774665}, {"id": 121871, "content": "我暂时最年轻⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 121872, "content": "期待你早点滚蛋，好安静的上位", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786701}, {"id": 121873, "content": "身材比他们好，空着的银行卡比他们多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785833}, {"id": 122129, "content": "拉屎可以半个多小时而且一天n次", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788002}, {"id": 122130, "content": "年轻的人也分很多种", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652491}, {"id": 121876, "content": "单纯简单，不会想的很复杂，喜欢就表达喜欢，不会像“老人”那样口是心非耍心眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668776}, {"id": 121877, "content": "那我也得先进职场再说啊?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786713}, {"id": 121878, "content": "不怎么肯接受别人的意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 121879, "content": "没有比我更年轻的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749608}, {"id": 122135, "content": "活力  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114275}, {"id": 121880, "content": "我就是新来的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786739}, {"id": 122136, "content": "都是留过洋的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761050}, {"id": 121881, "content": "已经沦为渣，感觉不再爱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408568}, {"id": 121882, "content": "眼高手低", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680045}, {"id": 124954, "content": "多才多艺，嚣张……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797632}, {"id": 121883, "content": "前面的等等我，我就是那个没断奶的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766851}, {"id": 121884, "content": "都长得挺好看的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273191}, {"id": 121885, "content": "我们怎么样要你们叨逼叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738384}, {"id": 121886, "content": "我就是个最年轻的\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786758}, {"id": 121887, "content": "我最年轻了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163956}, {"id": 122143, "content": "思维活跃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769338}, {"id": 121888, "content": "一个比一个智障 一个比一个会装", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626900}, {"id": 121889, "content": "想走就走", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786767}, {"id": 121890, "content": "百度用得更多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225023}, {"id": 121891, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786769}, {"id": 121892, "content": "心怀大海春暖花开", "image": "img/option/option/20161008162618k0Ipu7F2OdiVTSo8", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786767}, {"id": 121893, "content": "spy哦明明名额铃铃铃应该你你你，(⊙o⊙)哦(⊙o⊙)哦哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685181}, {"id": 121894, "content": "一代比一代差，大清药丸咯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729533}, {"id": 121896, "content": "毛都不会，工资一点也不少", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258708}, {"id": 121897, "co